From 6d0dbd309687113009a276886628c7c74c848d3c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Kees Cook <keescook@chromium.org>
Date: Tue, 24 Oct 2017 08:13:44 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] drm/i915/selftests: Convert timers to use timer_setup()
Git-commit: 6d0dbd309687113009a276886628c7c74c848d3c
Patch-mainline: v4.16-rc1
References: FATE#322643 bsc#1055900

In preparation for unconditionally passing the struct timer_list pointer to
all timer callbacks, switch to using the new timer_setup() and from_timer()
to pass the timer pointer explicitly.

